尼克·格里姆肖 (Nick Grimshaw) 在格拉斯顿伯里分享安妮·南丁格尔 (Annie Nightingale) 最喜欢的故事https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-grimshaw-shares-favourite-story-of-annie-nightingale-at-glastonbury-3573191?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nick-grimshaw-shares-favourite-安妮·南丁格尔在格拉斯顿伯里的故事Alex RigottiThu, 18 Jan 2024 18:47:28 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3573191 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安妮·南丁格尔·尼克·格里姆肖（摄影：Dave Benett/Getty Images for Claridge&#39;s；Dave M. Benett/Getty Images for Victoria &amp; Albert Museum）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>传奇电台 DJ 于 1 月 11 日去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-grimshaw-shares-favourite-story-of-annie-nightingale-at-glastonbury-3573191">尼克·格里姆肖 (Nick Grimshaw) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 分享的安妮·南丁格尔 (Annie Nightingale) 最喜欢的故事的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安妮·南丁格尔·尼克·格里姆肖（摄影：Dave Benett/Getty Images for Claridge&#39;s；Dave M. Benett/Getty Images for Victoria &amp; Albert Museum）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale-Nick-Grimshaw-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>尼克·格里姆肖 (Nick Grimshaw) 分享了他最喜欢的已故电台 DJ 安妮·南丁格尔 (Annie Nightingale) 的故事之一。</p><p>这位传奇的 BBC 播音员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/broadcasting-legend-annie-nightingale-dies-aged-83-3569896">于 1 月 11 日在“短暂患病”后去世</a>。她是 BBC Radio 1 任职时间最长的 DJ，也是该电台第一位女 DJ。</p><p>现在，她在第一广播电台的同事尼克·格里姆肖向安妮·麦克讲述了他最喜欢的安妮·南丁格尔的故事。格里姆肖说，故事发生在2000年代，当时DJ在格拉斯顿伯里<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury">音乐节香格里拉</a>。</p><p> “她最终和这些人聊天，然后坐在一辆铰接式卡车的后座上，”格里姆肖开始说道。 “他们决定关上后门，因为天气有点冷。他们正在聊天，现在是凌晨五点。她就像[假装看手表]“哦，我最好走了，现在已经很早了——早上 8 点或 9 点什么的……”</p><p> “他们打开后门，她就在伦敦”格里姆肖告诉震惊的麦克。 “卡车已经运输了四个小时，没有人注意到谁坐在卡车后面。她在拉德布罗克格罗夫！” </p><figure id="attachment_3569986" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3569986" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3569986" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270.jpg" alt="第一位 Radio 1 女 DJ 安妮·南丁格尔 (Annie Nightingale) 于 1970 年推出了两场新节目" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Annie-Nightingale@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3569986" class="wp-caption-text"> 1970 年，第一位 Radio 1 女 DJ 安妮·南丁格尔 (Annie Nightingale) 推出了两场新节目。图片来源：Peter Stone/Mirrorpix via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>自从南丁格尔去世的消息传出以来，人们一直在分享她的悼念和他们自己的故事。南丁格尔本人表示，她显然是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/annie-nightingale-once-revealed-she-was-the-first-person-to-interview-paul-mccartney-after-john-lennons-death-3570274">约翰·列侬去世后第一个与保罗·麦卡特尼交谈的人</a>。 “他想代表琳达（他已故的妻子琳达·麦卡特尼）、他自己、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yoko-ono">洋子（小野）</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治（哈里森）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈（斯塔尔）表示感谢，”</a>她回忆道。</p><p>与此同时，粉丝们回忆起她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-are-remembering-this-brilliant-story-of-a-bet-annie-nightingale-had-with-joe-strummer-3570072">与 The Clash 的乔·斯特鲁默 (Joe Strummer) 的高风险赌注</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/broadcasting-legend-annie-nightingale-dies-aged-83-3569896">在这里</a>查看所有对南丁格尔的致敬。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-grimshaw-shares-favourite-story-of-annie-nightingale-at-glastonbury-3573191">尼克·格里姆肖 (Nick Grimshaw) 在格拉斯顿伯里 (Glastonbury) 分享的安妮·南丁格尔 (Annie Nightingale) 最喜欢的故事的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
